	   <tr><td colspan=2>He is absolutely correct here.&nbsp;&nbsp;If you use the quests to powerlevel yourself, your skills will suffer.  Whilst we can raise our offensive and spellcasting skills quite easily, at higher levels defense raises VERY slowly and at high costs(either exp lost from dieing or huge downtime for the cleric healing you).<br><br>Remember that enchanters are almost always the first member of the group to die when things go bad...and remember that once the enchanter dies, things get MUCH worse for the temporary survivors.<br><br>The moral of the story - raise your defense.<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
